a selfie video at the time.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my skills\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 567}, {\"ngram\": \"a selfie video\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just do not get how.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like, I am so prepared that I do not know if I am overthinking.\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's getting to the point where it's becoming dangerous because I am getting lost on all of my floor skills.\\\"\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 812, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"my floor skills\", \"from\": 795, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I kinda felt like I was in jail with my own brain and body, just like, I just feel so ashamed,\\\" Biles recalled after her decision to stop competing.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"jail\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 846}, {\"ngram\": \"my own brain\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 864}, {\"ngram\": \"body\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 916}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, the most-decorated gymnast in history, said she struggled with the intense public scrutiny she faced for prioritizing her mental and physical health.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the most-decorated gymnast\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the intense public scrutiny\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1062}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental and physical health\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everywhere I went I felt like they could see 'loser' or 'quitter' across my head,\\\" she reflects in the series.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1234, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"loser\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"'quitter\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"my head\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"the series\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I always felt like everyone was staring at me, even if they were not.\\\"\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In hindsight, Biles believes she was experiencing \\\"a trauma response of everything that has happened\\\" Biles has testifiedthat she was one of more than 140 female athletes sexually abused by former USA Gymnastics team doctor Larry Nassar, who was convicted and sentenced in a Michigan state court to up to175 years in prison.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1506, \"end\": 1520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999960988264928, \"rank\": 3.901188710969822e-06, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1545, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"score\": 0.9635112472856006, \"rank\": 0.03787060381209406, \"text\": \"Larry Nassar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics_sex_abuse_scandal\"}, {\"begin\": 1584, \"end\": 1592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Michigan\", \"score\": 0.8512111716469581, \"rank\": 0.11817963196742602, \"text\": \"Michigan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http:/